[While the likelihood of intentional poisoning is
low, given the known fanaticism of football fans
on the eastern side of the Atlantic Pond,
stranger things have been known to occur. More
information on the outcome of the investigations
as to the etiology of this food poisoning event
would be gratefully appreciated. - Mod.MPP]
[The nature of the illness is unclear but likely
is either a viral gastroenteritis (probably
norovirus-related) or a toxin-induced process
such as from staphylococcal enterotoxin. - Mod.LL]
